ys.succinct.xml.dom

Class AbstractReadonlyNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • ys.succinct.xml.dom.AbstractReadonlyNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Node
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractSuccinctNode, AttributeTextImpl

    public abstract class AbstractReadonlyNode
extends Object
implements Node
    An abstract node that implements Node API that is common to the read-only nodes of the succinct DOM. This implementation takes care of the mutating methods mostly that are simply not supported.
    Author:
    Yauheni Shahun
